{"tid":1037121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★吳女士2010年從內地來港屈居80呎劏房 「有諗過跳樓死咗去算啦。」","createTime":"2019-02-25T16:52:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T12:30:54.000Z","uid":19454,"like":225,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":87,"replies":[{"pid":"7170d4ddcffd904381446395ee5ea674b97a43ab","tid":1037121,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T16:52:22.000Z","msg":"吳女士於2010年從內地來港，丈夫2015年去世後，她只可與女兒租住於香港仔的劏房單位，而居住面積更只得80呎，「食飯、煮飯、 沖涼、去廁所，都喺同一個地方...連企嘅地方都無。」而就讀中學的女兒，更只能於床上溫習、做功課，「有時會留喺學校做完先，但都唔可以日日留。」<br />\n<br />\n環境人流複雜 心理受煎熬<br />\n<br />\n居住環境固然惡劣，但複雜的居住環境令二人更感煎熬。吳女士憶述出門時，經常有陌生男子從旁邊的單位偷窺，令母女大感不安；而女兒更因此不敢獨自歸家，需要吳女士陪同才敢上樓，「住喺呢種環境會發癲。」輪候公屋六年，仍然毫無消息，面對惡劣的居住環境，吳女士束手無策，「有諗過跳樓死咗去算啦。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2481160/org/7724a67f809c7470ae897efd1dc52689.jpg/rrz7Y3Q7AUiLbCUJjb9OInqjgDNdcy5t8GK_lfBiv5U?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2481160%2Forg%2F7724a67f809c7470ae897efd1dc52689.jpg%2Frrz7Y3Q7AUiLbCUJjb9OInqjgDNdcy5t8GK_lfBiv5U%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=e8a75ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/299209/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B-%E5%85%A9%E6%AF%8D%E5%A5%B3%E5%B1%88%E5%B1%8580%E5%91%8E%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E8%90%8C%E8%BC%95%E7%94%9F%E5%BF%B5%E9%A0%AD-%E5%85%A5%E4%BD%8F%E9%81%8E%E6%B8%A1%E6%88%BF%E5%B1%8B%E8%A6%8B%E6%9B%99%E5%85%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F299209%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25AF%258D%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B1%2588%25E5%25B1%258580%25E5%2591%258E%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF%25E8%2590%258C%25E8%25BC%2595%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E9%25A0%25AD-%25E5%2585%25A5%25E4%25BD%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25B1%258B%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%259B%2599%25E5%2585%2589&d=%2BPHBpHGgTFxyg2LnQdSnfQjMv